    "description": "<strong>You have sixteen weeks before the town ends.</strong><br>Each week is comprised of your work at a local market, and buying what you need to survive. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735410/extras/0fa4930d05efb86e91a8d2b0571d994a.poster.avif?t=1665856181\" width=564 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735410/extras/0fa4930d05efb86e91a8d2b0571d994a.webm?t=1665856181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735410/extras/0fa4930d05efb86e91a8d2b0571d994a.mp4?t=1665856181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>The cost of dinner is always fluctuating with disaster.</strong><br>Purchase food, bribe your boss, even saving the game has a price. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735410/extras/280969c9d6e1d9b7e3fe3af291998eb2.poster.avif?t=1665856181\" width=564 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735410/extras/280969c9d6e1d9b7e3fe3af291998eb2.webm?t=1665856181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735410/extras/280969c9d6e1d9b7e3fe3af291998eb2.mp4?t=1665856181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>The narrative:</strong><br>A local cult has slain the tree with pale roots. Tragedy and disease consume the town as an abominable new tree grows. You exist among a dwindling population, forced to survive sixteen dark and strenuous weeks. <br><br><br><strong>Product features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Earn money depending on your performance at work. <br></li><li>Spend money to survive.<br></li><li>Speak with many crazy characters as the town succumbs to tragedy.<br></li><li>Keep your family alive.</li></ul>",
